::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica smiles, continuing down the corridor and tightening his arm 
around Desmonus. On the other side of her, Bloodystrike jerks his 
eyes back to her face, realizing he had been staring at a spot a bit 
below her neck for a little longer than was polite.

Suddenly the base shakes as it lands, throwing Reptilica and 
Bloodystrike to the ground.
